Are anyone else’s builds failing on the `test_translation` in `translation_utils`? I read a message above that it might be relying on google translate, so maybe the build machine is getting blocked by google? It’s happening in two different PRs for me, one of which is all experimental changes, and the other is some unrelated redactor changes.

Yes @Hari should have this updated by tomorrow morning. @Hari could you fix or comment out the test for now so we get our Travis tests to pass?
